===环境===
2015年，萨尔布里境内共有5家污染企业<ref name="pollution">{{Cite web|url=http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/pollution/salbris/ville-41232|title=Pollution à Salbris (41300)|accessdate=2019-12-21|author=linternaute|language=fr|publisher=linternaute|archive-date=2019-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191221195249/http://www.linternaute.com/actualite/pollution/salbris/ville-41232|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
